metadata.name: Are You Lost?
metadata.description:
Are You Lost?,  
Mixed Media,  
5400px X 7200px,  
2022,

First work in Post-Internet Consciousness series.  This series aims to utilize elements of found art through many images and memes from across the internet, post-internet art style, and the graphics freely provided by MOCA (the Museum of Crypto Art). The ultimate  goal is to explore internet identity through the hybridization of these elements. ð“‚€
